msgid "Hello %(username)s!"
msgstr "Hej %(username)s!"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_email.txt:5
msgid ""
"Welcome to Suchar Overflow - a place where air humidity drops below zero."
msgstr ""
"Välkommen till Suchar Overflow – en plats där luftfuktigheten sjunker under "
"noll."

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_email.txt:6
msgid ""
"To make sure you're not a bot (or a person without a sense of humor), you "
"need to activate your account."
msgstr ""
"För att säkerställa att du inte är en robot (eller en person utan humor) "
"måste du aktivera ditt konto."

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_email.txt:8
msgid "Click this link before it dries out:"
msgstr "Klicka på den här länken innan den försvinner:"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_email.txt:11
msgid "Remember: Drink plenty of water."
msgstr "Kom ihåg: Drick mycket vatten."

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_email.txt:13
msgid "The Suchar Overflow Team"
msgstr "Suchar Overflow-teamet"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_failed.html:6
#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_failed.html:24
msgid "Activation Failed"
msgstr "Aktivering misslyckades"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_failed.html:26
msgid ""
"The activation link is invalid or has expired. Please try registering again "
"or contact support."
msgstr ""
"Aktiveringslänken är ogiltig eller har gått ut. Försök att registrera dig "
"igen eller kontakta supporten."

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/activation_failed.html:29
